title: Kerry community celebrates St Brigid with annual Biddy
desc: The origins of the annual Biddy - its members dressed in white and sporting flamboyant hats made out of oaten straw - is unknown, but is believed to be linked to centuries old customs celebrating the goddess/St Brigid, and the arrival of spring (Imbolc).

title: AC Milan goalkeeper Mike Maignan signs new deal to 2031
desc: AC Milan secured the long-term future of Mike Maignan after the goalkeeper signed a new deal to 2031 on Saturday. Maignan had an immediate impact after joining Milan from Lille in 2021 to replace Gianluigi Donnarumma, who left to Paris Saint-Germain. The France international helped Milan win Serie A in his first season and was named Serie A goalkeeper of the season.

title: Algal bloom brings 'sense of grief' to parts of Yorke Peninsula
